{"data": {"repository": {"pullRequest": {"id": "MDExOlB1bGxSZXF1ZXN0NTEwNjg5MjU5", "number": 9244, "title": "feat: defer deferrable endpoint calls on network failure", "bodyText": "Fixes #9231", "createdAt": "2020-10-27T11:42:16Z", "url": "https://github.com/vaadin/flow/pull/9244", "merged": true, "mergeCommit": {"oid": "29dbd0200939a1b9efa6116b41ff8cf54389247c"}, "closed": true, "closedAt": "2020-10-29T18:51:00Z", "author": {"login": "haijian-vaadin"}, "timelineItems": {"totalCount": 7, "pageInfo": {"startCursor": "Y3Vyc29yOnYyOpPPAAABdWncbVgH2gAyNTEwNjg5MjU5OmY3ZGUzODRmN2ZkN2E0MmJjZmQxYTI3ZjA3ZWU5MTJmNWIzYjE1YmE=", "endCursor": "Y3Vyc29yOnYyOpPPAAABdXThC3gH2gAyNTEwNjg5MjU5OmY0NjkxMWFlMmFkMWM3NDdjOTE1MzQwNzc0YzQyNTIwMjg4Mjk3ZDk=", "hasNextPage": false, "hasPreviousPage": false}, "nodes": [{"__typename": "PullRequestCommit", "commit": {"oid": "f7de384f7fd7a42bcfd1a27f07ee912f5b3b15ba", "author": {"user": {"login": "haijian-vaadin", "name": "Haijian Wang"}}, "url": "https://github.com/vaadin/flow/commit/f7de384f7fd7a42bcfd1a27f07ee912f5b3b15ba", "committedDate": "2020-10-27T11:40:55Z", "message": "feat: defer deferrable endpoint calls on network failure"}}, {"__typename": "PullRequestReview", "id": "MDE3OlB1bGxSZXF1ZXN0UmV2aWV3NTE4NTQ3NDQy", "url": "https://github.com/vaadin/flow/pull/9244#pullrequestreview-518547442", "createdAt": "2020-10-28T11:06:55Z", "commit": {"oid": "f7de384f7fd7a42bcfd1a27f07ee912f5b3b15ba"}, "state": "CHANGES_REQUESTED", "comments": {"totalCount": 1, "pageInfo": {"startCursor": "Y3Vyc29yOnYyOpK0MjAyMC0xMC0yOFQxMTowNjo1NVrOHpk16A==", "endCursor": "Y3Vyc29yOnYyOpK0MjAyMC0xMC0yOFQxMTowNjo1NVrOHpk16A==", "hasNextPage": false, "hasPreviousPage": false}, "nodes": [{"id": "MDI0OlB1bGxSZXF1ZXN0UmV2aWV3Q29tbWVudDUxMzM1NzI4OA==", "bodyText": "In Firefox the error message is different: NetworkError when attempting to fetch resource.\nThis tells me that checking a message string is unreliable.\nI\u2019d suggest to check against the errors we throw ourselves instead:\nif ((error instanceof EndpointResponseError) || (error instanceof EndpointError)) {\n  // Error thrown in the client, carry to the user\n  throw error;\n} else {\n  // Network error\n  return this.cacheEndpointRequest({endpoint, methods, params});\n}\n\nThis is safer: if it\u2019s not the error we throw ourselves, then it\u2019s a fetch error, which is only thrown for the network reasons.", "url": "https://github.com/vaadin/flow/pull/9244#discussion_r513357288", "createdAt": "2020-10-28T11:06:55Z", "author": {"login": "platosha"}, "path": "flow-client/src/main/resources/META-INF/resources/frontend/Connect.ts", "diffHunk": "@@ -339,12 +339,18 @@ export class ConnectClient {\n     params?: any,\n   ): Promise<DeferrableResult<any>> {\n     if (this.checkOnline()) {\n-      const result = await this.call(endpoint, method, params);\n-      return { isDeferred: false, result };\n+      try {\n+        const result = await this.call(endpoint, method, params);\n+        return { isDeferred: false, result };\n+      } catch (error) {\n+        if (error.message === 'Failed to fetch') {", "state": "SUBMITTED", "replyTo": null, "originalCommit": {"oid": "f7de384f7fd7a42bcfd1a27f07ee912f5b3b15ba"}, "originalPosition": 10}]}}, {"__typename": "PullRequestCommit", "commit": {"oid": "96b379d2bc8e919aae691c2067cefd800d8638c5", "author": {"user": {"login": "haijian-vaadin", "name": "Haijian Wang"}}, "url": "https://github.com/vaadin/flow/commit/96b379d2bc8e919aae691c2067cefd800d8638c5", "committedDate": "2020-10-28T11:18:10Z", "message": "Merge branch 'feature/offline' into haijian/defer-on-unreachable-server"}}, {"__typename": "PullRequestCommit", "commit": {"oid": "a4d8a1e75caa367e08c04c79c94576cfc8ab7534", "author": {"user": {"login": "haijian-vaadin", "name": "Haijian Wang"}}, "url": "https://github.com/vaadin/flow/commit/a4d8a1e75caa367e08c04c79c94576cfc8ab7534", "committedDate": "2020-10-28T11:22:54Z", "message": "use more reliable error check for network errors